542
00:27:01.100 --> 00:27:02.560
The more I write...

543
00:27:03.230 --> 00:27:04.940
the more my stomach growls!

544
00:27:06.150 --> 00:27:07.810
There's no stoppin' these ideas!

545
00:27:07.810 --> 00:27:09.400
I ain't got time to eat!

546
00:27:09.400 --> 00:27:12.030
I need you to chow down for me, York!

547
00:27:13.780 --> 00:27:16.410
Okay!

548
00:27:20.120 --> 00:27:23.540
That's the ticket! My noggin
is soakin' up the nutrients!

549
00:27:23.540 --> 00:27:25.870
I've got even more ideas!

550
00:27:26.960 --> 00:27:29.290
Eat! Eat! York!

551
00:27:30.750 --> 00:27:33.550
Another helping for you, Dr. York.

552
00:27:38.010 --> 00:27:40.010
Nuh-uh, not enough!

553
00:27:40.010 --> 00:27:41.760
Get me more!

554
00:27:41.760 --> 00:27:44.350
Yes, doctor! Right away!

555
00:27:52.320 --> 00:27:54.610
Yummy!

556
00:27:54.610 --> 00:27:57.570
Her current BMI is over 600!

557
00:27:57.570 --> 00:27:59.820
I don't want any more!

558
00:28:00.780 --> 00:28:02.990
That's it, S-Shark!

559
00:28:02.990 --> 00:28:06.460
The battle data keeps updating!

560
00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:11.420
Oh no, not now...!

561
00:28:15.170 --> 00:28:19.050
Ow, ow... I'm calling a temporary truce!

562
00:28:19.640 --> 00:28:22.640
I can't miss this opportunity
to monitor his growth!

563
00:28:23.720 --> 00:28:26.600
I gotta go to the bathroom,
but I can't waste any time!

564
00:28:33.570 --> 00:28:35.280
Much better!

565
00:28:36.950 --> 00:28:40.490
Digestion Punch!

566
00:28:43.280 --> 00:28:45.410
That's it! Time to experiment!

567
00:28:45.410 --> 00:28:48.370
Please bring me all materials
relating to devil fruits!

568
00:28:48.370 --> 00:28:51.000
Deliver everything to Dr. Pythagoras!

569
00:28:51.000 --> 00:28:52.750
Prep for Dr. Edison's experiment!

570
00:28:52.750 --> 00:28:55.260
To simulation room 88!

571
00:28:56.630 --> 00:28:57.840
Nap time.

572
00:29:00.590 --> 00:29:04.890
That's Dr. York's fourth
snack, dump, nap cycle today!

573
00:29:14.770 --> 00:29:15.780
Are you serious?!

574
00:29:24.080 --> 00:29:25.910
That's enough, seraphim.

575
00:29:25.910 --> 00:29:26.740
Stand down.

576
00:29:27.790 --> 00:29:29.870
Edison, Lilith, Pythagoras!

577
00:29:30.330 --> 00:29:31.750
I think you've had enough.

578
00:29:31.750 --> 00:29:33.840
Oh, what a shame...

579
00:29:33.840 --> 00:29:35.590
Consarn it!

580
00:29:35.590 --> 00:29:36.960
Ouch!

581
00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:38.630
Why's that scoundrel butting in?!

582
00:29:38.630 --> 00:29:40.680
We were just getting to the good part!

583
00:29:40.680 --> 00:29:42.300
Eureka!

584
00:29:51.350 --> 00:29:54.230
Did that guy come to rescue us?

585
00:29:54.230 --> 00:29:56.610
No way, he's just as shady
as the rest of them!

586
00:29:56.610 --> 00:29:59.110
He's probably a colleague of Lilith's.

587
00:29:59.110 --> 00:30:01.610
So this guy must be...

588
00:30:01.610 --> 00:30:04.530
I am Dr. Vegapunk Shaka.

589
00:30:04.950 --> 00:30:04.990
Shaka the Just

